quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,The emulous desire of abundance engrosseth you
  102,2,Until ye visit the graves
  102,3,Lo! presently ye shall know
  102,4,Again lo! presently ye shall know
  102,5,Lo! would that ye knew now with the surety of knowledge
  102,6,Surely ye shall behold theScorch
  102,7,Then ye shall surely beholdwith the surety of vision
  102,8,"Then, on that Day, ye shall surely be asked of the delights"